2164.subject: MLML
2164.descrlong:
MLML 131:Marine Botany-  Covers plants of the sea, marshes, and dunes emphasizing the morphology, taxonomy, and natural history of seaweeds and vascular plants. Offered through Moss Landing Marine Laboratories (MLML); contact SEP program office for MLML registration procedures.

(Prereq: Include Junior and Senior and Post Bac and Graduate)
